{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Firefox 27 für Entwickler","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/27","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox developer release notes</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases\">Firefox developer release notes</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Add-ons</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/Add-ons/WebExtensions\">Browser extensions</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/Add-ons/Themes\">Themes</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Firefox internals</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/\">Mozilla project</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Gecko\">Gecko</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Headless_mode\">Headless mode</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/JavaScript_code_modules\">JavaScript code modules</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/js-ctypes\">JS-ctypes</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/MathML_Project\">MathML project</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/MFBT\">MFBT</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Projects\">Mozilla projects</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Preferences\">Preference system</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/WebIDL_bindings\">WebIDL bindings</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XPCOM\">XPCOM</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL\">XUL</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Building and contributing</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions\">Build instructions</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/Configuring_Build_Options\">Configuring build options</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Build_Instructions/How_Mozilla_s_build_system_works\">How the build system works</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Developer_guide/Source_Code/Mercurial\">Mozilla source code</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Localization\">Localization</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Mercurial\">Mercurial</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/QA\">Quality assurance</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Using_Mozilla_code_in_other_projects\">Using Mozilla code in other projects</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div><div class=\"overheadIndicator draft draftHeader\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>Diese Seite ist noch nicht fertig.</strong>\n<div id=\"sect3\">Firefox 27 ist noch keine vollständige Version. Neue Features werden demnächst hinzugefügt.</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Möchten Sie helfen Firefox 27 zu dokumentieren? Schauen Sie auf die <a href=\"http://beta.elchi3.de/doctracker/#list=fx&amp;version=27.0\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><span class=\"external\">Liste von Bugs, über die geschrieben werden sollte</span></a> und schreibe Sie dazu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"änderungen_für_web-entwickler","title":"Änderungen für Web-Entwickler","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>Keine Änderung.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Die Element <code>grab</code> und <code>grabbing</code> der Eigenschaft <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/cursor\"><code>cursor</code></a> sind nunmehr ohne Präfix (<code>-moz-grab</code> und <code>-moz-grabbing</code>).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/ECMAScript_6_support_in_Mozilla\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">EcmaScript 6</a> (Harmony)<span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"alt-edited hps\"> Implementierung</span></span> wird fortgeführt!</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Der Harmony <a href=\"http://wiki.ecmascript.org/doku.php?id=harmony:spread\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Spread Operator</a> ist nun in der Funktion calls verfügbar. (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=762363\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;762363</a>)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfacesapisdom","title":"Interfaces/APIs/DOM","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>Keine Änderung.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mathml","title":"MathML","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>Keine Änderung.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"svg","title":"SVG","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>Keine Änderung.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veränderungen_für_addon-_und_mozilla-entwickler","title":"Veränderungen für AddOn- und Mozilla-Entwickler","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Der <code>downloads-indicator</code>-Button wurde entfernt. Das Element <code>downloads-button</code> sollte nun verwendet werden. <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"alt-edited hps\">Wenn Sie prüfen möchten</span><span>, dass es seine</span> <span class=\"hps\">Overlay</span> <span class=\"alt-edited hps\">geladen hat</span><span>,</span> <span class=\"alt-edited hps\">überprüfen Sie das <code>indicator</code></span>-<span class=\"hps\">Attribut</span> <span class=\"alt-edited hps\">auf diesen Button</span> <span class=\"alt-edited hps\">.</span></span></li>\n <li>Das <code>chrome://browser/skin/downloads/indicator.css-</code>Stylesheet ist nicht länger in Firefox referenziert.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/27/Site_Compatibility\"><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"alt-edited hps\">Seiten-</span><span>Kompatibilität</span> <span class=\"hps\">für</span> <span class=\"hps\">Firefox</span> <span class=\"hps\">27</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ältere_versionen","title":"Ältere Versionen","isH3":true,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"multiColumnList\" id=\"sect4\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/26\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 26 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/25\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 25 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/24\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 24 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 23 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 22 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/21\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 21 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/20\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Firefox 20 for developers (en-US)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/19\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in Eng